WEBVTT

00:11.480 --> 00:12.280
Not long after

00:12.800 --> 00:15.480
Nandu City fell

00:42.640 --> 00:43.520
You're still here

00:44.840 --> 00:45.720
I've always been here

00:49.960 --> 00:51.080
No matter what the outcome

00:53.080 --> 00:55.400
I will face it together with Your Majesty

00:58.960 --> 01:01.720
Great Xuan's accumulation over decades

01:03.280 --> 01:04.640
Now destroyed in one fire

01:06.040 --> 01:07.960
It is my fault

01:10.640 --> 01:12.720
Since ancient times, rulers die with their state

01:13.840 --> 01:15.080
As long as I am here

01:17.320 --> 01:19.320
Great Xuan will not be humiliated

01:24.840 --> 01:25.920
Your Majesty still has a sword

01:28.640 --> 01:29.720
Has heroic spirit

01:30.840 --> 01:31.640
And me

01:35.160 --> 01:36.600
They say Chen and Sikong

01:37.520 --> 01:38.480
Rule the realm together

01:39.960 --> 01:40.640
Now

01:42.520 --> 01:43.720
It is Chen and Sikong

01:45.640 --> 01:46.960
Facing survival and destruction together

01:50.960 --> 01:52.160
Arm me

01:53.840 --> 01:54.400
Yes

01:55.760 --> 01:56.280
Miss Chen

01:56.960 --> 01:57.720
What a coincidence

01:58.320 --> 01:59.400
I am here on my granduncle's orders

01:59.640 --> 02:01.080
To report to His Majesty

02:07.280 --> 02:07.840
Miss Chen

02:08.400 --> 02:09.400
My benefits

02:10.040 --> 02:11.160
Aren't they a bit lacking?

02:11.640 --> 02:13.040
A mutually beneficial matter

02:13.280 --> 02:14.400
What else does Your Highness want?

02:14.960 --> 02:15.960
My friendship

02:17.400 --> 02:18.480
Does Your Highness dare to want it?

02:23.080 --> 02:24.720
You traitor

02:26.960 --> 02:28.160
Look at our ancestors

02:28.520 --> 02:29.520
Think about what you've done

02:31.520 --> 02:33.080
Do you still know your surname?

02:33.960 --> 02:34.760
Chen

02:37.280 --> 02:38.160
This is for Your Highness

02:38.920 --> 02:39.600
For the Chen family

02:40.280 --> 02:41.200
And for the realm

02:42.080 --> 02:43.160
The best outcome

02:58.080 --> 02:58.960
Are you afraid?

03:00.400 --> 03:01.280
With Your Majesty here

03:02.760 --> 03:03.280
I'm not afraid

03:09.640 --> 03:11.040
Beat the drums for me

03:11.840 --> 03:13.520
I will protect Great Xuan

03:14.200 --> 03:15.920
Until the end

03:22.720 --> 03:24.080
Corpses fill the palace

03:24.200 --> 03:25.640
Blood fills the streets

03:26.080 --> 03:28.960
This is the integrity Xuan Kingdom lacked for decades

03:29.720 --> 03:31.200
The capital's sun

03:32.280 --> 03:33.160
Has set
